# Python-generated files
__pycache__/
*.py[oc]
build/
dist/
wheels/
*.egg-info

# Virtual environments
.venv/

# Test cache
.pytest_cache/

# Secrets -- nothing in this repo currently reads an env var (no
# os.getenv/os.environ anywhere in src/, confirmed 2026-07-14 pre-publish
# audit), so there is no live secret to leak today. Excluded anyway as a
# standing guard for whenever that changes (e.g. a Socrata app token).
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# Raw downloads and derived data — never committed (see PLAN.md Global Constraints).
# Anchored to the repo root (leading /): an unanchored "data/" also matched
# web/src/data/ -- confirmed live, this silently kept web/src/data/examples.ts
# (a real source file the app imports and the demo depends on) out of every
# commit since it was written. A fresh clone of this repo was missing it
# entirely; `git ls-files | grep examples.ts` returned nothing before this fix.
/data/
